---
title: Thai Veggie Noodles (v)
description: Travel to Thailand without leaving your kitchen. Packed with vegetables like bok choy, green beans and bright red pepper, and full of fragrant flavours like ginger, chilli and coconut milk, this is a dish that will take your stir-fry game to new levels of deliciousness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-veggie-noodles-554ce8fd-6e357959.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/thai-veggie-noodles-5b48a5d9ae08b568e9627ec2-d7e19c86.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/thai-veggie-noodles-5b48a5d9ae08b568e9627ec2
time required: 30 minutes
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
cuisine: Asian
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 495 kcal
